/Helvetica findfont
42 scalefont 
setfont

1 0 0 setrgbcolor                           % Set the color to red
35 400 moveto
( Linux Gazette) show                       % Print "Linux Gazette"

1 0.8 0.6 setrgbcolor                       % Sets the color to orange
35 400 moveto
1 1 4 { 300 0 rlineto -300 10 rmoveto } for %for loop to draw the lines
stroke

showpage

